hopobject.body: Canada>Canada alpha gpc vs cdp choline reddit Lots of insoluble fiber, conversely, can make things a whole lot worse (particularly if it's not balanced out by some soluble fiber), exacerbating a pre-existing tendency toward urgent, loose bowel movements. For these patients, it can be helpful to think of soluble fiber as the "anchor" of each meal, ensuring that a fruit, veggie, grain and/or seed rich in soluble fiber plays a starring role in the mix.
